            <scopecontent id="aspace_36f9a3285eae1c277d6cb29388bd0112">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Consists of James T. Babb's gift of Strong material which includes Babb's correspondence with Strong and his wife, Sylvia; Strong's outgoing correspondence with friends and colleagues; and manuscripts and typescripts of essays, poems, short stories, and notes. The material also includes Babb's correspondence with the dealer Bertram Rota, from whom he acquired his collection, and the artist J. Howard Lewis.</p>
            </scopecontent>
